OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1779120673
OL,3,CFacial recognition to be used in
OL,4,Cpolicing operation of protests and FA
OL,5,CCup final
OL,7,FA massive policing operation on a
OL,8,Fscale "unprecedented in recent years"
OL,9,Fis being planned as two protest
OL,10,Fmarches and the FA Cup final take
OL,11,Fplace in London on Saturday.
OL,13,FThousands of officers will take to the
OL,14,Fstreets and armoured vehicles will be
OL,15,Fdeployed along with police horses,
OL,16,Fdogs, drones and helicopters as the
OL,17,FMet aims to avoid clashes between
OL,18,Fgroups of protesters.
OL,26,@pD@GOUpD@eO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/11
