PN,40902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1779120673
OL,3,CFacial recognition to be used in
OL,4,Cpolicing operation of protests and FA
OL,5,CCup final
OL,7,FHeavy restrictions have been put in
OL,8,Fplace in a bid to keep the Unite the
OL,9,FKingdom and pro-Palestine Nakba Day
OL,10,Frallies separate, with added concerns
OL,11,Fthat some football fans will go
OL,12,Fstraight from the FA Cup final to the
OL,13,FTommy Robinson event.
OL,15,FFor the first time under official
OL,16,Fprotest restrictions, organisers of
OL,17,Fthe rallies will face prosecution as
OL,18,Fwell as any speakers who break the law
OL,19,Fby using the events as a platform for
OL,20,Fextremism or hate speech.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1779120673
OL,3,CFacial recognition to be used in
OL,4,Cpolicing operation of protests and FA
OL,5,CCup final
OL,7,FLive facial recognition will be used
OL,8,Ffor the first time in a policing
OL,9,Foperation around a protest, with
OL,10,Fcameras set up in a location in Camden
OL,11,Fthat is not on the route of the Unite
OL,12,Fthe Kingdom march, but is expected to
OL,13,Fbe used by a lot of people attending
OL,14,Fthe event.
OL,16,FThere remain more than 50 outstanding
OL,17,Fand unidentified suspects after
OL,18,Fviolent clashes between police and
OL,19,Fprotesters at the previous Unite the
OL,20,FKingdom event in September.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1779120673
OL,3,CFacial recognition to be used in
OL,4,Cpolicing operation of protests and FA
OL,5,CCup final
OL,7,FMetropolitan Police Deputy Assistant
OL,8,FCommissioner James Harman said the
OL,9,Fscale of the operation is
OL,10,F"unprecedented in recent years" and
OL,11,Fwill cost the force #4.5 million, #1.7
OL,12,Fmillion of which is to bring in
OL,13,Fofficers from other forces to boost
OL,14,Fnumbers.
OL,16,FAround 4,000 officers are expected to
OL,17,Fbe on duty on Saturday, with 660 being
OL,18,Fdrafted in from forces outside the Met.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@_O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1779120673
OL,3,CFacial recognition to be used in
OL,4,Cpolicing operation of protests and FA
OL,5,CCup final
OL,7,FMr Harman said: "We are policing two
OL,8,Fsignificant and potentially
OL,9,Fchallenging protests in the centre of
OL,10,FLondon, as well as the FA Cup final,
OL,11,Fwhich is taking place in Wembley on
OL,12,Fthe same day.
OL,26,@oD@QOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1779120673
OL,3,CFacial recognition to be used in
OL,4,Cpolicing operation of protests and FA
OL,5,CCup final
OL,7,F"We're doing this at a time of
OL,8,Fcontinued global instability and
OL,9,Ftension, which we know has the
OL,10,Fpotential to fuel tension and play out
OL,11,Fon the streets of London, the
OL,12,Fterrorism threat level has been raised
OL,13,Fto severe, and in recent weeks and
OL,14,Fmonths, we have seen a terrorist
OL,15,Fattack.
OL,17,F"We've seen a sustained campaign of
OL,18,Farson targeting Jewish Londoners,
OL,19,Fagainst the backdrop of increasing
OL,20,Fhate crime, in particular antisemitism.
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1779120673
OL,3,CFacial recognition to be used in
OL,4,Cpolicing operation of protests and FA
OL,5,CCup final
OL,7,F"So fears in Jewish communities are
OL,8,Fparticularly heightened, but we've
OL,9,Falso seen increased concern more
OL,10,Fbroadly, including in Muslim
OL,11,Fcommunities.
OL,13,F"Taken together, these factors give us
OL,14,Fsignificant cause for concern as we
OL,15,Fhead into the weekend, and require a
OL,16,Fpolicing plan that provides us with
OL,17,Fthe most assertive grip on the
OL,18,Fmovement of large numbers of people,
OL,19,Flarge groups, and the potential for
OL,20,Fserious disorder and other criminality
OL,21,Fthat may arise as a result."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU}D@\O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/11
