CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1779120673
OL,3,CFacial recognition to be used in
OL,4,Cpolicing operation of protests and FA
OL,5,CCup final
OL,7,FEarlier this week Prime Minister Sir
OL,8,FKeir Starmer said he would block "far-
OL,9,Fright agitators" from coming to the UK
OL,10,Ffor the Unite the Kingdom march which
OL,11,Fhe said was "designed to confront and
OL,12,Fintimidate... this diverse country".
OL,14,FSo far the Home Office has blocked
OL,15,Fseven people from travelling to
OL,16,FBritain from overseas for the event.
OL,18,FPolice estimate around 50,000 people
OL,19,Fwill attend the Unite the Kingdon
OL,20,Frally, with 30,000 at Nakba Day
OL,26,@pD@bOUqD@PO]sD@MOUtD@cO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/11
